parameters:
You chatty pig! Blabbering on and on... Intruder!
Don't think you can escape!

Damn! Is this a modified soldier... It seems
difficult to escape... Shuu! Give me instructions!

※After this, a choice will appear. Do you want to
save? (Depending on the choice, it may result in
game over)
We have to find a way to escape!
どうにかして逃げるんだ！
Ugh!? Can't be helped then, in times like this...

It's useless against me who possesses super
regeneration abilities!
Buy us some time! I'll figure something out!
Hmph! It's fine if I defeat him, right...!

You're doing quite well! But how long can you last
in front of me with my super regeneration ability?

It seems like we'll have enough goods this time...
With the President and many executives present, we
can't afford to fail.
Can you tell me more about that?

What!? Who are you! How did you get in!? No, I
must call security...
Whoa, stay still or I'll cut your throat.
A, a cyborg...! P, please stop, don't kill me!

So, will you tell me about the conversation from
earlier? Shuu, is the communication okay?

So you're testifying about the auction, confirming
that human trafficking is real.

Yes, it's true. Among the imperial elites, owning
a human as a pet is a kind of status symbol. The
rarer the human you own, the more you can boast
about it.

There are various differences in human appearances
too...

That's disgusting... So when is the auction taking
place?

It's next week... Every year... On that day,
President Waltin's birthday...

Esuka, we should wrap this up soon, we might be
spotted by the enemy.

Just one last thing! Do you know a girl named
Mikoto?

No, I don't remember every pet's name... But, I
think there was a pet with that name owned by the
President...
Hey! Speak clearly! I can't hear you!
R-report! The resistance has launched an attack!
